[{"author":null,"categories":["绝活！必看榜！"],"content":null,"date":1036022400,"description":"","dir":"post/","excerpt_html":null,"excerpt_text":null,"expirydate":-62135596800,"fuzzywordcount":200,"html":null,"keywords":null,"kind":"page","lang":"en","lastmod":1036022400,"objectID":"6ba7a14b5f9cb9182391c3e5e2723e2a","permalink":"https://Yuhang-Harry-Gao.github.io/post/hello-world/","publishdate":"2002-10-31T00:00:00Z","readingtime":1,"relpermalink":"/post/hello-world/","section":"post","summary":"\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026ldquo;学计算机一定要有一个非常强大的心理状态。什么呢？计算机的所有东西都是人做出来的，别人能想出来的我也能一定能想的出来。在计算机里头没有任何黑魔法，所有的东西只不过是我现在不知道而已。总有一天我会把所有的细节，所有的内部的东西全部搞明白了。\u0026rdquo;\u003cbr\u003e\n—— \u003ca href=\"https://person.zju.edu.cn/wengkai\"\u003e翁恺\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","tags":["Computer Science"],"title":"Hello World!","type":"post","url":"/post/hello-world/","weight":-1000,"wordcount":143},{"author":null,"categories":["LLM"],"content":null,"date":1749513600,"description":"","dir":"post/","excerpt_html":null,"excerpt_text":null,"expirydate":-62135596800,"fuzzywordcount":700,"html":null,"keywords":null,"kind":"page","lang":"en","lastmod":1749513600,"objectID":"5fd15d877479172ef241c19002f071be","permalink":"https://Yuhang-Harry-Gao.github.io/post/ai-studio/","publishdate":"2025-06-10T00:00:00Z","readingtime":2,"relpermalink":"/post/ai-studio/","section":"post","summary":"\u003cp\u003e这篇blog简单说说怎么设置 AI studio 的 Run settings(界面右侧的面板)吧，具体细节去看\u003ca href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/ai-studio-quickstart\"\u003eGoogle AI Studio quickstart\u003c/a\u003e: \u003ca href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/ai-studio-quickstart\"\u003ehttps://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/ai-studio-quickstart\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"简介\"\u003e简介\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e利用 \u003cstrong\u003eGoogle AI Studio\u003c/strong\u003e ，可以快速尝试各种模型，使用不同的提示进行试验。准备好构建后，可以选择“获取代码”和首选编程语言，以使用 Gemini API。(——叽里咕噜说啥呢？)\u003c/p\u003e","tags":["AI","Gemini","Google"],"title":"Google AI Studio 的参数设置","type":"post","url":"/post/ai-studio/","weight":0,"wordcount":650},{"author":null,"categories":["从0开始的机器学习生活"],"content":null,"date":1749168000,"description":"","dir":"post/","excerpt_html":null,"excerpt_text":null,"expirydate":-62135596800,"fuzzywordcount":600,"html":null,"keywords":null,"kind":"page","lang":"en","lastmod":1749168000,"objectID":"e78cac39f9d55e00333882970dcd0f69","permalink":"https://Yuhang-Harry-Gao.github.io/post/diffusion/","publishdate":"2025-06-06T00:00:00Z","readingtime":2,"relpermalink":"/post/diffusion/","section":"post","summary":"\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026ldquo;The sculpture is already complete within the marble block, before I start my work. It is already there, I just have to chisel away the superfluous material.\u0026quot;—— Michelangelo\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e写这篇blog是为了记录自己的学习过程。我认为: 如果我不能把知识写成文字, 那就说明我也没理解。\u003cbr\u003e\n希望最后这篇 blog 能够顺便帮助 0 基础的朋友学习。\u003cbr\u003e\n特别希望收到各位大佬的帮助和指导!\u003c/p\u003e","tags":["AI","Machine Learning","Diffusion"],"title":"Diffusion mini-tutorial","type":"post","url":"/post/diffusion/","weight":0,"wordcount":573},{"author":null,"categories":null,"content":null,"date":-62135596800,"description":"","dir":"about/","excerpt_html":null,"excerpt_text":null,"expirydate":-62135596800,"fuzzywordcount":100,"html":null,"keywords":null,"kind":"page","lang":"en","lastmod":-62135596800,"objectID":"8576ec274c98b3831668a172fa632d80","permalink":"https://Yuhang-Harry-Gao.github.io/about/","publishdate":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","readingtime":1,"relpermalink":"/about/","section":"","summary":"\u003ch2 id=\"about-me\"\u003eAbout Me\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHi, I am \u003cstrong\u003eYuhang Gao\u003c/strong\u003e, an undergraduate student from the Class of 2025, majoring in Information Systems and Information Management \u003ca href=\"https://www.xjtlu.edu.cn/\"\u003eXi’an Jiaotong-Liverpool University\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e","tags":null,"title":""